title: Age of Empires II - Win10 compatible - All patches/patches
description:
Age of Empires II - Complete Pack v2
--------------------------------------

Windows 8.1 and Windows 10 compatible


This torrent contains:

- Age of Empires II - Age of Kings
- Age of Empires II - The Conquerors Expansion
- 1.0e Patch for Conquerors Expansion
- Age of Empires II - Forgotten Empires (Inofficial Expansion)
- Wippien (a free VPN client that runs smoothly with Age of Empires)

The inofficial expansion "Forgotten Empires" contains:

-More nations
-Maximum population limit is set to 1000 (instead of 200 in the official versions)
-Some bugs were fixed --> It runs smoothly on Windows 7 or 8.
-Higher resolutions can be set (up to 1900x1200 and higher)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Release notes:
Release Note:
--------------
-The game is playable on Windows 10, if you install all patches included in this package.
-The basic version "Age of Empires II - Age of Kings" is _not_ cracked and thus not playable. Additionaly, the basic version crashes on Windows 10.
-Anyway "Age of Kings" needs to be installed to play "Age of Conquerors" or "Age of Forgotten Empires" expansions.
-The included VPN tool Wippien is just one method to play with your friends via a virtual network. You can also use tools like Hamachi, Tunngle, etc. or meet in real life and play in a real cabled network.
